        <button class="btn-mini" onclick="_popoutStudy()" title="Open in a separate window. If it opens as a tab, your browser's 'open new pages as tabs' preference is overriding the popup hint (Safari → Tabs → 'Open pages in tabs instead of windows' → set to 'Manually').">Pop out &#8599;</button>
        <button class="btn-mini" onclick="_closeStudyEmbedded()" title="Close">&times;</button>
      </div>
